> Looking to round out your Dad's Day meal? This kit has everything you need to make a delicious, hearty avocado cheddar ranch salad. Don't be surprised when you find him asking for this combo of cruciferous veggies, dried fruit, seeds, fried onions, and cheddar cheese on the regular.

Empty contents of @Avocado Cheddar Ranch Salad Kit{12%ounce} into a #large bowl{}. Drizzle with as much dressing as you like, then toss to evenly coat.